wallaby track
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:the open road, chiefly in phrase on the wallaby (track): tramping the country as a swagger
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
See:
Pronunciation:
Notes: (orig. and mainly Aust [AND 1849]) on the wallaby, on the wallaby track
